<body>
        <div class="mains">
            <p>
                As a college student, most of us have attempted to make a delicious drink and have ended up with a pretty foul concoction. This is a guide to making tastier drinks so you can enjoy a refreshing drink at home instead of spending lots of money at the bars.
            </p>
        </div>
        <div class="forms">
            <form action="/search" target="POST">
                <p>Please fill out the form below. If you have more than one of these items, separate it by commas.</p>
                Alcohol Type:<br>
                <input type="text" name="alcohols" placeholder="Vodka">
                <br>
                Other Ingredients:<br>
                <input type="text" name="ingredients" placeholder="Orange juice, Sprite">
                <br> Difficulty: <br>
                <form class="input-field">
                    <input type="radio" name="difficulty" value="very-easy"> Very Easy<br>
                    <input type="radio" name="difficulty" value="easy"> Easy<br>
                    <input type="radio" name="difficulty" value="medium"> Medium <br>
                    <input type="radio" name="difficulty" value="hard"> Hard <br>
                </form>
                <br> Rating: <br>
                <select class="input-field">
                    <option value="" disabled selected>Select</option>
                    <option value="1">1</option>
                    <option value="2">2</option>
                    <option value="3">3</option>
                    <option value="4">4</option>
                    <option value="4">5</option>
                </select><br>
                <input type="submit" value="Submit">
            </form>
        </div>
    </body>